      <title>解决Github Pages搭建的个人博客无法访问的问题</title>
      <link href="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>最近一段时间，发现使用Hexo+Github搭建的个人博客部署后无法访问</p><p>显示如下</p><ul><li>火狐浏览器</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Snipaste_2020-09-05_15-00-26.png" alt="Snipaste_2020-09-05_15-00-26"></p><p>点击“接受风险后继续”，显示空白</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Snipaste_2020-09-05_14-58-35.png" alt="Snipaste_2020-09-05_14-58-35"></p><ul><li>谷歌浏览器</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Snipaste_2020-09-05_14-59-55.png" alt="Snipaste_2020-09-05_14-59-55"></p><hr><h3 id="问题原因"><a href="#问题原因" class="headerlink" title="问题原因"></a>问题原因</h3><p>经常访问github 的小伙伴都知道，这个通常是域名解析的问题，DNS解析</p><p>于是ping一下这个地址：</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/image-20200905152708910.png" alt="image-20200905152708910"></p><p>发现DNS都被解析为127.0.0.1，怪不得无法访问，那么问题就很容易解决了。</p><h3 id="解决办法"><a href="#解决办法" class="headerlink" title="解决办法"></a>解决办法</h3><p>在<a href="https://www.ipaddress.com中查询对应的真实ip地址/">https://www.ipaddress.com中查询对应的真实IP地址</a></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Snipaste_2020-09-05_15-29-28.png" alt="Snipaste_2020-09-05_15-29-28"></p><p>复制其中一个真实IP地址</p><p>在C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc目录的hosts文件中，添加配置：IP地址 域名</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/05/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/image-20200905153412006.png" alt="image-20200905153412006"></p><p>保存后，重新访问即可。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
