    <entry>
      <title>Wndows10系统激活</title>
      <link href="/2020/09/02/Wndows10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%BF%80%E6%B4%BB/"/>
      <url>/2020/09/02/Wndows10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%BF%80%E6%B4%BB/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>Windows10系统存在激活（许可证）时间，一旦许可证即将过期，系统就会提示如下信息：</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/02/Wndows10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%BF%80%E6%B4%BB/image-20200902210807825.png" alt="image-20200902210807825"></p><p>通过以下方式查看许可证过期时间：</p><p>win+r打开运行窗口，输入</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">slmgr.vbs -dlv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>显示如下：</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/09/02/Wndows10%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%BF%80%E6%B4%BB/image-20200902211243383.png" alt="image-20200902211243383"> </p><hr><h4 id="激活Window10系统"><a href="#激活Window10系统" class="headerlink" title="激活Window10系统"></a>激活Window10系统</h4><p>以激活win10专业版为例，打开cmd，输入以下命令：</p><ul><li>安装密钥</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">slmgr &#x2F;ipk W269N-WFGWX-YVC9B-4J6C9-T83GX</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>设置kms服务器</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">slmgr &#x2F;skms zh.us.to</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>激活win10专业版系统</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">slmgr &#x2F;ato</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
