      <title>Hexo-搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h3 id="一-下载与安装Git"><a href="#一-下载与安装Git" class="headerlink" title="一. 下载与安装Git"></a>一. 下载与安装Git</h3><h4 id="1-下载"><a href="#1-下载" class="headerlink" title="1.下载"></a>1.下载</h4><p>​        Git官网网址为: <a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com</a></p><p>点击Downloads</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818074822924.png" alt="image-20200818074822924"></p><p>选择Windows版本</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818074916174.png" alt="image-20200818074916174"></p><p>选择64位版本</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818075734543.png" alt="image-20200818075734543"></p><h4 id="2-安装"><a href="#2-安装" class="headerlink" title="2.安装"></a>2.安装</h4><p>​        一直点击Next即可.</p><h4 id="3-配置"><a href="#3-配置" class="headerlink" title="3.配置"></a>3.配置</h4><h5 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h5><ul><li>配置Git用户名与邮箱</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git  config --global  user.name  <span class="string">&#x27;GitHub用户名&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">git  config --global  user.email  <span class="string">&#x27;GitHub邮箱&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="参考文档"><a href="#参考文档" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h6><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/ximiaomiao/p/7140456.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/ximiaomiao/p/7140456.html</a></p><h5 id="生成SSH-Key并连接GitHub"><a href="#生成SSH-Key并连接GitHub" class="headerlink" title="生成SSH Key并连接GitHub"></a>生成SSH Key并连接GitHub</h5><p>在 Git Bash中执行以下命令</p><ul><li>查看是否存在SSH key</li></ul><p>​       检查本机用户home目录中是否存在SSH Key，如果存在则跳到第三步</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>创建SSH Key</li></ul><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh<span class="literal">-keygen</span> <span class="literal">-t</span> rsa <span class="literal">-C</span> <span class="string">&quot;GitHub邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​            提示输入SSH Key文件存储路径，直接回车（选择默认路径）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">which</span> to save the key (/c/Users/Lenovo/.ssh/id_rsa):</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​            提示输入密码，直接回车（空密码）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty <span class="keyword">for</span> no passphrase):</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​            提示确认密码，直接回车</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​            提示密码生成信息</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Your identification has been saved <span class="keyword">in</span> /c/Users/Lenovo/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved <span class="keyword">in</span> /c/Users/Lenovo/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">SHA256:/MJjjpNCdfM/MAafADt/gxqDMLewnrdOEi0MoVviUj4 824491225@qq.com</span><br><span class="line">The key<span class="string">&#x27;s randomart image is:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">+---[RSA 3072]----+</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|.                |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|..    .          |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|+ o    o         |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|.O+.. +.=        |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|o.E*.+ +SB .     |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|. .++ o.o.X      |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">| ..o.  ==o.=     |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|  ooo ++ o  o    |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|   ooo...    .   |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">+----[SHA256]-----+</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>在GitHub添加SSH Key</p><ul><li><p>拷贝SSH Key</p><p>在Git Bash中执行命令:</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clip &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>设置GitHub的SSH Key</p><ul><li>选择Settings</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818083941997.png" alt="image-20200818083941997"></p><ul><li>选择SSH and GPG keys，点击New SSH Key</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818084203191.png" alt="image-20200818084203191"></p><ul><li>在Key中粘贴SSH Key，并点击Add SSH Key</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818084419732.png" alt="image-20200818084419732"></p></li></ul></li><li><p>测试SSH Key</p><p>在Git Bash中执行命令</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh <span class="literal">-T</span> git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​        提示信息1:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The authenticity of host <span class="string">&#x27;github.com (207.97.227.239)&#x27;</span> can<span class="string">&#x27;t be established.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">RSA key fingerprint is 16:27:ac:a5:76:28:2d:36:63:1b:56:4d:eb:df:a6:48.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Are you sure you want to continue connecting (yes/no)?</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​            输入yes，提示</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hi username! You＇ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​        提示信息2:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hi username! You＇ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="参考文档-1"><a href="#参考文档-1" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h6><p><a href="https://www.xuanfengge.com/using-ssh-key-link-github-photo-tour.html">https://www.xuanfengge.com/using-ssh-key-link-github-photo-tour.html</a></p><h3 id="二-下载与安装Node-js"><a href="#二-下载与安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="二. 下载与安装Node.js"></a>二. 下载与安装Node.js</h3><h4 id="1-下载-1"><a href="#1-下载-1" class="headerlink" title="1.下载"></a>1.下载</h4><p>​        Node.js官网网址为:<a href="https://nodejs.org/">https://nodejs.org</a></p><p>选择LTS版本</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818090345443.png" alt="image-20200818090345443"></p><h4 id="2-安装-1"><a href="#2-安装-1" class="headerlink" title="2.安装"></a>2.安装</h4><p>​        一直点击Next即可.</p><h4 id="3-测试"><a href="#3-测试" class="headerlink" title="3.测试"></a>3.测试</h4><p>​        打开Git Bash，输入node -v查看版本</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node <span class="literal">-v</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="三-初始化Hexo"><a href="#三-初始化Hexo" class="headerlink" title="三. 初始化Hexo"></a>三. 初始化Hexo</h3><p>​    在Git Bash中执行命令</p><ul><li><p>安装淘宝镜像源</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install <span class="literal">-g</span> cnpm -<span class="literal">-registry</span>=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>查看cnpm版本</li></ul><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm <span class="literal">-v</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装Hexo</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install <span class="literal">-g</span> hexo<span class="literal">-cli</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>查看Hexo版本</li></ul><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="literal">-v</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>新建blog文件夹，在文件夹中使用Git Bash</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818121220884.png" alt="image-20200818121220884"></p></li><li><p>初始化Hexo</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>初始化成功提示信息</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Cloning hexo-starter https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-starter.git</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Install dependencies</span><br><span class="line">added 183 packages from 420 contributors and audited 189 packages <span class="keyword">in</span> 21.577s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">8 packages are looking <span class="keyword">for</span> funding</span><br><span class="line">  run `npm fund` <span class="keyword">for</span> details</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">found 0 vulnerabilities</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start blogging with Hexo!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>开启Hexo</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>localhost:4000访问</p></li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818122040040.png" alt="image-20200818122040040"></p><h3 id="四-部署Hexo到GitHub"><a href="#四-部署Hexo到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="四. 部署Hexo到GitHub"></a>四. 部署Hexo到GitHub</h3><p>​        在blog文件夹下使用Git Bash</p><ul><li>安装hexo部署插件</li></ul><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -<span class="literal">-save</span> hexo<span class="literal">-deployer</span><span class="literal">-git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>在GitHub中创建Repository</p><ul><li>选择New repository</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818130526011.png" alt="image-20200818130526011"></p><ul><li>Repository name:  GitHub用户名.github.io</li><li>Description: 可选</li><li>点击Create repository</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818130814276.png" alt="image-20200818130814276"></p><ul><li>拷贝SSH</li></ul></li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818130859522.png" alt="image-20200818130859522"></p><ul><li><p>配置部署</p><p>在blog根目录的_config.yml中配置如下信息</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> [<span class="string">新建仓库的SSH</span>]</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>部署</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>测试</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2020/08/18/Hexo-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200818131553976.png" alt="image-20200818131553976"></p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
